  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/2d3b1a5d0fe9a60e7290c2a735b3ecff.poster.avif?t=1700096747\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/2d3b1a5d0fe9a60e7290c2a735b3ecff.webm?t=1700096747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/2d3b1a5d0fe9a60e7290c2a735b3ecff.mp4?t=1700096747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>It's garbage night, and there's no human in sight! Explore neighbourhoods of Toronto as the unofficial mascot of the city: the <strong><i>Trash Panda</i></strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make a Mess!</h2>As a mischievous raccoon, make the biggest mess you can knocking over trash bins lining the streets. The bigger the mess, the higher you score. Some of the trash is yummy-yummy treats giving you additional points. Find power-ups too!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/75abecf8731beddb3a1bc9357f35b48f.poster.avif?t=1700096747\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/75abecf8731beddb3a1bc9357f35b48f.webm?t=1700096747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/75abecf8731beddb3a1bc9357f35b48f.mp4?t=1700096747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the Real-World Streets of Toronto</h2>The maps of Trash Panda are created from real-world street data of Canada's most populous city. See if you can visit every street on the map!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/3328d10a72d734711e76b85e674d5d10.poster.avif?t=1700096747\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/3328d10a72d734711e76b85e674d5d10.webm?t=1700096747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/3328d10a72d734711e76b85e674d5d10.mp4?t=1700096747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenges!</h2>Some crescents and dead-end streets are home to territorial raccoons that don't want you knocking over their bins. Should you enter these areas, a nemesis raccoon may challenge you to a match! Which of you can knock over the most bins? Winner takes all!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/0884d9ffd220969045b3b4dd4d9c823a.poster.avif?t=1700096747\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/0884d9ffd220969045b3b4dd4d9c823a.webm?t=1700096747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/0884d9ffd220969045b3b4dd4d9c823a.mp4?t=1700096747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/2d3b1a5d0fe9a60e7290c2a735b3ecff.poster.avif?t=1700096747\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/2d3b1a5d0fe9a60e7290c2a735b3ecff.webm?t=1700096747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/2d3b1a5d0fe9a60e7290c2a735b3ecff.mp4?t=1700096747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>It's garbage night, and there's no human in sight! Explore neighbourhoods of Toronto as the unofficial mascot of the city: the <strong><i>Trash Panda</i></strong>.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Make a Mess!</h2>As a mischievous raccoon, make the biggest mess you can knocking over trash bins lining the streets. The bigger the mess, the higher you score. Some of the trash is yummy-yummy treats giving you additional points. Find power-ups too!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/75abecf8731beddb3a1bc9357f35b48f.poster.avif?t=1700096747\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/75abecf8731beddb3a1bc9357f35b48f.webm?t=1700096747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/75abecf8731beddb3a1bc9357f35b48f.mp4?t=1700096747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Explore the Real-World Streets of Toronto</h2>The maps of Trash Panda are created from real-world street data of Canada's most populous city. See if you can visit every street on the map!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/3328d10a72d734711e76b85e674d5d10.poster.avif?t=1700096747\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/3328d10a72d734711e76b85e674d5d10.webm?t=1700096747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/3328d10a72d734711e76b85e674d5d10.mp4?t=1700096747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Challenges!</h2>Some crescents and dead-end streets are home to territorial raccoons that don't want you knocking over their bins. Should you enter these areas, a nemesis raccoon may challenge you to a match! Which of you can knock over the most bins? Winner takes all!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/0884d9ffd220969045b3b4dd4d9c823a.poster.avif?t=1700096747\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/0884d9ffd220969045b3b4dd4d9c823a.webm?t=1700096747\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1669320/extras/0884d9ffd220969045b3b4dd4d9c823a.mp4?t=1700096747\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
